title: [LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan - 701 - The Raven Mystery Train
description:
A train whistle blows in the distance. This dark train encapsulates Haibara, sealing her in enemy territory. The only destination -- danger and sorrow. The shadows of the Organization loom ever closer, watching her every move. The long awaited Mystery Train arc on the Bell Tree Express begins with a bang bang bang. All aboard.

- LucarioPK Subs
